<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xml:lang="en"><generator uri="https://gohugo.io/" version="0.74.3">Hugo</generator><title type="html">metadata on krei</title><link href="https://krei.projects.metio.wtf/tags/metadata/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="HTML"/><link href="https://krei.projects.metio.wtf/tags/metadata/index.xml" rel="alternate" type="application/rss+xml" title="RSS"/><link href="https://krei.projects.metio.wtf/tags/metadata/atom.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" title="Atom"/><updated>2020-08-16T02:31:00+00:00</updated><id>https://krei.projects.metio.wtf/tags/metadata/</id><entry><title type="html">Metadata</title><link href="https://krei.projects.metio.wtf/contributors/metadata/?utm_source=atom_feed" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id>https://krei.projects.metio.wtf/contributors/metadata/</id><published>2020-04-13T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2020-04-13T00:00:00+00:00</updated><content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Every contributor may add/remove her/his metadata to the <a href="https://github.com/metio/krei/tree/master/krei-docs/data/contributors">list of contributors</a> at any time.</p>
<p>Metadata is currently used in three places:</p>
<ol>
<li>To generate a list of existing <a href="https://jedisct1.github.io/minisign/">minisign</a> signatures in the <a href="../first-timer">first timer</a> documentation.</li>
<li>To generate a <a href="http://humanstxt.org/">humans.txt</a> file of <a href="https://krei.projects.metio.wtf/humans.txt">all contributors</a>.</li>
<li>To generate a <a href="http://www.foaf-project.org/">FOAF</a> for the <a href="https://krei.projects.metio.wtf/foaf.rdf">entire project</a>.</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="adding-a-new-entry">Adding a new entry</h2>
<p>Create a new file called <code>&lt;YOUR_NAME&gt;.yaml</code> in the <a href="https://github.com/metio/krei/tree/master/krei-docs/data/contributors">contributors directory</a>. Add the following properties to it:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="chroma"><code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"><span class="k">id</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s1">&#39;&lt;YOUR_NAME&gt;&#39;</span><span class="w">                   </span><span class="c"># should match file name (required)</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="w"></span><span class="k">minisign</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s1">&#39;&lt;YOUR_MINISIGN_PUB_KEY&gt;&#39;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="c"># used for key verification (required)</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="w"></span><span class="k">title</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s1">&#39;&lt;YOUR_TITLE&gt;&#39;</span><span class="w">               </span><span class="c"># used by FOAF/humans.txt (optional)</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="w"></span><span class="k">first_name</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s1">&#39;&lt;YOUR_FIRST_NAME&gt;&#39;</span><span class="w">     </span><span class="c"># used by FOAF/humans.txt (optional)</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="w"></span><span class="k">last_name</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s1">&#39;&lt;YOUR_LAST_NAME&gt;&#39;</span><span class="w">       </span><span class="c"># used by FOAF/humans.txt (optional)</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="w"></span><span class="k">email</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s1">&#39;&lt;YOUR_EMAIL&gt;&#39;</span><span class="w">               </span><span class="c"># used by FOAF (optional)</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="w"></span><span class="k">website</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s1">&#39;&lt;YOUR_URL&gt;&#39;</span><span class="w">               </span><span class="c"># used by FOAF/humans.txt (optional)</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre></div>]]></content><category scheme="https://krei.projects.metio.wtf/categories/contributors" term="contributors" label="Contributors"/><category scheme="https://krei.projects.metio.wtf/tags/metadata" term="metadata" label="metadata"/></entry></feed>